item.title: Looking and Moving Forward
item.author: me@aaron-torres.com (Aaron Torres)
item.description: I wanted to start this year off with a new blog built on top of Github Pages and Jekyll, and a look back on what went well (and didn’t) in 2013. The Job The single biggest event of this year was completely uprooting our lives, packing up, and leaving the state. We did this with a car full of a few clothes, a box of important documents, a laptop, 1 cat, 1 dog, 1 baby, and 2 adult humans.
